<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.3">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="en"/><updated>2024-05-30T17:12:57+00:00</updated><id>https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><subtitle>Napon Jatusripitak&apos;s personal website </subtitle><entry><title type="html">The Thai Senate: A Crisis of Representation in the Making | FULCRUM</title><link href="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/the-thai-senate-a-crisis-of-representation-in-the-making-fulcrum/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="The Thai Senate: A Crisis of Representation in the Making | FULCRUM"/><published>2024-05-27T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-05-27T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/the-thai-senate-a-crisis-of-representation-in-the-making--fulcrum</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/the-thai-senate-a-crisis-of-representation-in-the-making-fulcrum/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The convoluted selection process and the likelihood of self- or vested interests overshadowing public ones in Thailand’s senatorial race mean that the odds of a truly representative body are slim.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Political Stakes of Pheu Thai’s 10,000 Baht Digital Wallet Initiative | FULCRUM</title><link href="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/political-stakes-of-pheu-thais-10000-baht-digital-wallet-initiative-fulcrum/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Political Stakes of Pheu Thai’s 10,000 Baht Digital Wallet Initiative | FULCRUM"/><published>2024-05-02T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-05-02T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/political-stakes-of-pheu-thais-10000-baht-digital-wallet-initiative--fulcrum</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/political-stakes-of-pheu-thais-10000-baht-digital-wallet-initiative-fulcrum/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The Pheu Thai Party is seeking to push through its 10,000 baht digital wallet scheme. If it fails, there would be significant ramifications for the party. Yet, even if it succeeds, there is no guarantee that the party will regain its electoral dominance.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Pheu Thai Versus Bank of Thailand: More Than a Question of Digital Wallets and Interest Rates | FULCRUM</title><link href="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/pheu-thai-versus-bank-of-thailand-more-than-a-question-of-digital-wallets-and-interest-rates-fulcrum/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pheu Thai Versus Bank of Thailand: More Than a Question of Digital Wallets and Interest Rates | FULCRUM"/><published>2024-03-19T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-03-19T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/pheu-thai-versus-bank-of-thailand-more-than-a-question-of-digital-wallets-and-interest-rates--fulcrum</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/pheu-thai-versus-bank-of-thailand-more-than-a-question-of-digital-wallets-and-interest-rates-fulcrum/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A festering dispute between the Pheu Thai-led government and the Bank of Thailand has underscored a major question as to who sets the kingdom’s economic direction.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Move Forward Stands at the Brink of Dissolution | FULCRUM</title><link href="https://naponjatusripitak.github.io/blog/2024/move-forward-stands-at-the-brink-of-dissolution-fulcrum/" re